Automate your CV in R Markdown: Easy as 1, 2, knit! 🧶

Go from data to professional CV using R Markdown. This repository stores the slides and materials for the workshop “Automate your CV: easy as 1, 2, knit!” presented at the R-Ladies Melbourne meetup in Feb 2022.

View the slides at shaziaruybal.github.io/automate-cv-rmd

Watch the talk recording on Youtube

Materials

datadrivencv materials

  • cv.rmd: this is the edited CV .rmd document created during the workshop. To view, click here.
  • kate_dibiasky_datadrivencv.pdf: this is the CV created during the workshop. Download Kate’s CV here.
